WEBVTT

00:00:05.061 --> 00:00:13.121
I bow to all the seekers of Truth.

00:00:22.737 --> 00:00:28.777
I had also told you earlier in
Yamuna Nagar what the Truth is.

00:00:30.388 --> 00:00:36.238
When we seek without knowing the
Truth, we go astray.

00:00:36.965 --> 00:00:48.525
Especially in Haryana I see, that
there is a huge market of gurus
settled here.

00:00:48.525 --> 00:00:53.932
Gurus of all kinds are living here.
Some are of one kind, some of another.

00:00:53.932 --> 00:01:01.723
Some give a name to someone, while
some tell someone to chant for so
many days.

00:01:01.848 --> 00:01:09.058
If there's nothing new happening, then
they say, "Well, you give me this much
money, then you'll be fine."

00:01:10.020 --> 00:01:18.410
Those who do all these trades should
know that there cannot be any
business of God.

00:01:18.410 --> 00:01:21.546
And whoever does will have to pay dearly.

00:01:21.546 --> 00:01:30.094
But even those who go to them are
deeply saddened. They get badly
destroyed.

00:01:30.335 --> 00:01:39.555
I saw a gentleman had just arrived
in Chandigarh, was all wrinkled.

00:01:39.555 --> 00:01:42.490
A young man, he was all wrinkled.

00:01:43.121 --> 00:01:49.571
Met another gentleman who started telling,
"I have been giving money to this
Radha Swami for fourteen years."

00:01:49.571 --> 00:01:54.919
I didn't find anything, and I'm so
sick, I can't walk, my arms and
legs are shaking."

00:01:55.006 --> 00:02:00.556
Oh, the guru who can't even give
you your health and robs you of
your money,

00:02:00.556 --> 00:02:04.379
at least think with your intellect too.

00:02:04.471 --> 00:02:08.551
You are intelligent people. What
kind of influence do gurus have?

00:02:09.658 --> 00:02:15.408
So, the first thing I'm going to tell
you today, is how to recognize a Guru
– is a very important thing.

00:02:15.408 --> 00:02:18.094
Because its market is set up here.

00:02:18.638 --> 00:02:26.618
That day there were at least 40 to 50
people in Kurukshetra who were absolutely
struck by gurus.

00:02:27.727 --> 00:02:30.227
And a few gurus also came with them.

00:02:31.495 --> 00:02:37.025
They have no fear of God.
They want to befool.

00:02:37.775 --> 00:02:42.135
It's okay if they just take money.
They're ruining your Kundalini.

00:02:42.135 --> 00:02:47.404
They ruin your health, children die.
All sorts of things happen.

00:02:48.046 --> 00:02:52.376
And what they do is spiritism,
crematorium devilry.

00:02:53.314 --> 00:02:59.484
Everybody in our country knows about
black magic. There is something called
black magic, everybody knows it.

00:02:59.795 --> 00:03:08.045
And by doing that, they're destroying people.
On one side they're destroying people, and
making a lot of money for themselves.

00:03:08.174 --> 00:03:10.844
But their mind(intellect) is completely
upside down.

00:03:10.844 --> 00:03:14.893
Even a dirty man like Rajneesh is
held in high esteem by the people.

00:03:15.071 --> 00:03:22.591
Tell Me, the one who has no place in any
country, who is such a filthy man that
even mentioning his name is filth,

00:03:22.591 --> 00:03:27.637
I don't understand how people in India
can think highly of such a man.

00:03:27.637 --> 00:03:34.717
He lives in Poona, but no Indians
come there. They come from your
place, from Haryana.

00:03:37.486 --> 00:03:42.536
I've heard, people drink alcohol here,
and they're searching for all the
(UNCLEAR) in alcohol.

00:03:42.536 --> 00:03:46.717
When man gets money, then he does
something or the other like this

00:03:46.717 --> 00:03:49.983
so that he may be destroyed. Should
think of some good work as well.

00:03:50.634 --> 00:03:56.934
What's done is done. But now these
gurus are completely bad.

00:03:57.065 --> 00:04:06.305
Once they stick, can't get rid of them.
- now, this is the first thing.

00:04:07.412 --> 00:04:16.302
He did all this simply by mesmerizing
people and making them forget,

00:04:16.302 --> 00:04:18.483
that they just couldn't see what all
they were doing.

00:04:18.483 --> 00:04:24.805
And now after this, along with
their (UNCLEAR) and with their
tongues and with their heart

00:04:24.805 --> 00:04:31.293
when they went to him, there were
four cameras installed. And the
four cameras caught it.

00:04:31.612 --> 00:04:34.902
Because you can't mesmerize the cameras.

00:04:36.076 --> 00:04:39.496
They can't be misguided as these
people have been.

00:04:39.496 --> 00:04:44.416
And even after being caught, people still
believe in him. It's a very sad thing.

00:04:44.838 --> 00:04:50.618
There is devotion within us, there is
a search within us, we are searching
for the Truth.

00:04:50.676 --> 00:04:56.256
What did Nanak Sahib say? "Guru is
the one who unites you to the Lord."

00:04:56.256 --> 00:05:00.166
A Guru is one who talks about
uniting us with God.

00:05:00.199 --> 00:05:07.329
Those who talk nonsense like, "Give
this much money, do this, serve me,"
these people are not gurus.

00:05:08.507 --> 00:05:15.947
Gave all the wrong mantras. Not everyone
has the right to give mantras also.

00:05:15.948 --> 00:05:19.328
And which mantra should be given,
there is a science for that too.

00:05:19.390 --> 00:05:22.670
What will happen even if a donkey
gets up and gives some mantras?

00:05:23.536 --> 00:05:27.866
Your those (UNCLEAR) who came here, they
gave the mantra Inga, Pinga and Thinga.

00:05:27.866 --> 00:05:34.805
Tell me which mantras are these? And
he said, "Don't tell anyone, with
great difficulty I told you."

00:05:34.805 --> 00:05:40.016
This shouldn't be told to anyone. These
poor, simple foreigners don't know
anything about Inga, Pinga or Thinga.

00:05:40.911 --> 00:05:46.691
Kept saying the same mantra for years.
They went mad, developed epilepsy,
and their condition worsened.

00:05:46.730 --> 00:05:51.550
Now, later on, started saying that
you didn't move around in this
(UNCLEAR - Manner?).

00:05:52.289 --> 00:05:54.989
You (UNCLEAR) what's the use/what
will be achieved?

00:05:55.572 --> 00:06:00.102
As it is cars are a problem, and on
top of that, with everyone jumping
around - what's the need for this?

00:06:00.102 --> 00:06:07.914
What have you come to achieve? What
do you want to achieve? You want to
know the Truth, right?

00:06:09.248 --> 00:06:21.068
So what is the Truth? You are not the
body, the mind, these emotions,
these values, none of these.

00:06:21.252 --> 00:06:28.502
You are the Pure Spirit. Firstly,
know that when you say,

00:06:28.502 --> 00:06:35.871
'This is my body, this is my intellect,'
so who is this 'I'? Should know that 'I'.

00:06:36.146 --> 00:06:40.796
And to know that I-I, you
don't have to do anything.

00:06:40.808 --> 00:06:45.988
You have all the preparations within
you as described. Kundalini is to be
awakened.

00:06:46.628 --> 00:06:49.688
But now there is no need to go to
these false(misleading) gurus.

00:06:49.688 --> 00:06:54.555
One gentleman started saying that,
"Mother, I will also practice Sahaja Yoga
and go to the fake Gurus as well."

00:06:55.035 --> 00:07:00.265
So then I said, "If you put one foot
in the crocodile's mouth, how will
you get into My boat?"

00:07:01.547 --> 00:07:08.457
But you know this very well, you are not
[UNCLEAR] I would say, you are innocent,

00:07:09.115 --> 00:07:17.145
so, in your innocence, you go there. But
leave it now, all these things are useless.

00:07:17.145 --> 00:07:20.801
You've been doing the same thing
for years, and will keep doing
it on for years.

00:07:20.801 --> 00:07:25.040
Well, did you get anything from this?
You should think about it first.

00:07:29.399 --> 00:07:33.909
So I spoke about it today because
when I came back after travelling
all around Haryana,

00:07:34.235 --> 00:07:39.135
then I came to know that there's
more than required network of the
false gurus here.

00:07:39.594 --> 00:07:43.384
