though they may have just been
released from jail.

00:07:47.821 --> 00:07:53.283
Didn't find out who was the father,
who was the mother, nothing, and
have no knowledge, nothing.

00:07:53.283 --> 00:07:58.359
This Rajneesh didn't even know Sanskrit.
He's completely a useless man.

00:08:00.312 --> 00:08:06.172
