people here, one is this, then another
is that, then another is that.

00:08:06.359 --> 00:08:12.139
Don't know why, perhaps because people
of Haryana used to live more in the
countryside earlier,

00:08:12.139 --> 00:08:17.682
it's possible that's why everyone is
so simple-hearted. They thought,
'First catch me only.'

00:08:18.480 --> 00:08:22.820
No where are there so many false
gurus as there are here.

00:08:25.172 --> 00:08:29.172
