was Dr. Talwar.

00:08:29.310 --> 00:08:35.940
His guru, started a fight in the
entire house, took away everyone's
property, did everything.

00:08:35.940 --> 00:08:39.852
Then to these people didn't understand
how much harm was caused to them.

00:08:40.463 --> 00:08:47.163
She used to say, "What is all this
wealth? It's nothing but dust.
Give it to me."

00:08:47.163 --> 00:08:50.910
Oh, if it's dust for these humans,
then it should be ashes for you.

00:08:50.910 --> 00:08:53.995
(UNCLEAR) Sitting there as an ascetic.

00:08:54.565 --> 00:09:00.312
So, all of you should become cautious.
I want - there has been a lot of
awakening in Yamuna Nagar,

00:09:00.312 --> 00:09:03.436
