in that way.

00:09:03.436 --> 00:09:07.748
As soon as money comes to you,
just like a fly goes to jaggery,

00:09:07.748 --> 00:09:12.811
similarly, all these gurus will
rip you off in one way or another.

00:09:12.811 --> 00:09:16.131
Not only money, they will destroy
in every way.

00:09:16.779 --> 00:09:21.329
You will get cancer, you will get
all sorts of diseases, you will
get heart attacks;

00:09:21.329 --> 00:09:26.203
I have seen all the disciples
of Bala Swami, Radha Swami.
They have heart problems.

00:09:26.203 --> 00:09:30.046
Whosoever you see has a heart problem.
Young men get heart attacks.

00:09:30.046 --> 00:09:34.916
Well, your guru is very great. Said,
"Sir, I'm big, have an organization."

00:09:34.916 --> 00:09:38.622
What are we supposed to do with it?
Even thieves can have an organization.

00:09:40.061 --> 00:09:43.951
As a Mother, I want to tell you today

00:09:43.951 --> 00:09:48.825
that there's no need to go to any
guru - I'll make you your own guru.

00:09:48.825 --> 00:09:54.634
Yes, there have been. I'm not saying there
haven't been gurus - there have been many real
gurus, but there's a way to identify them.

00:09:54.634 --> 00:09:58.179
What have his disciples achieved?

00:09:58.940 --> 00:10:05.150
What have they received? What are
they like, we should see that.
We should see how they behave.

00:10:06.191 --> 00:10:09.631
Then you will know how the gurus
themselves behave.

00:10:09.631 --> 00:10:13.826
It's the guru only who instills such
things in our minds. They are the ones who
run (carry on) such pursuits of the world.

00:10:20.158 --> 00:10:25.308
So, you should just remain (UNCLEAR)
aloof from all these things, give them up,

00:10:25.308 --> 00:10:30.724
should be finished. It's very important
if your children are also going to it.

00:10:30.724 --> 00:10:38.801
This land of Haryana is so lush
and green, so sometimes it feels scary

00:10:38.801 --> 00:10:43.349
that if these evil people destroyed it,
what will happen to the people here?

00:10:46.259 --> 00:10:51.889
Now the other thing I want to tell is
that, the second Truth is that all
around spread

00:10:51.889 --> 00:10:58.001
this Conscious Power, is Itself the
love of God — is the Supreme Love.

00:10:58.594 --> 00:11:06.624
Selfless, God loves you so much,
He has such a passion for you.

00:11:08.298 --> 00:11:15.028
Until you understand the passion of
that God, you will continue to do
all wrong things of the world.

00:11:15.028 --> 00:11:20.341
Like someone said, "I fast for God."
Now think over, that God,

00:11:20.745 --> 00:11:29.315
He is your Father. Which father
would want his child to fast?

00:11:30.195 --> 00:11:36.638
And which Mother would that be - on the
contrary, when we are angry with our
mothers, then we fast to trouble them.

00:11:37.390 --> 00:11:41.790
So, leave all these fasting etc, penance
and chanting(spiritual practices) of the world.

00:11:42.236 --> 00:11:46.116
Leave them and attain your Pure Spirit.

00:11:46.143 --> 00:11:51.863
Because God Almighty is the embodiment
of love, and His kingdom awaits you.

00:11:51.875 --> 00:11:55.475
You come and be seated in it

00:11:55.475 --> 00:11:59.924
and what all are His Blessings,
be nourished with them.

00:11:59.924 --> 00:12:05.630
Having received those blessings, may
you enjoy happiness, peace and joy.

00:12:07.308 --> 00:12:15.288
This is the only desire of God,
and it can only happen when you
are united with Him.

00:12:15.756 --> 00:12:19.866
With this Power, with the Power of
God Almighty, how will you be connected?

00:12:20.442 --> 00:12:30.572
Just as there is this thing to connect
this instrument, similarly, there is a
Power within you called Kundalini.

00:12:30.572 --> 00:12:40.433
