the six chakras and connects you

00:12:40.433 --> 00:12:47.315
with the All-Pervading Power of God's
love; Then there is a complete
transformation within you.

00:12:47.874 --> 00:12:53.254
A person becomes so beautiful,
as if he is an angel.

00:12:53.328 --> 00:12:59.698
His life becomes so beautiful, he
becomes quite like an angel of god.

00:13:00.122 --> 00:13:07.452
Everything is so wonderful, and
the greatest thing about it is

00:13:07.452 --> 00:13:11.465
that it's your own power that's
working out.

00:13:11.506 --> 00:13:17.286
This power, which is your own, awakens.
Your own power heals you.

00:13:17.286 --> 00:13:20.080
I have nothing to do with that.

00:13:20.338 --> 00:13:24.228
One lamp is lit, and then it can
enlighten many more lamps.

00:13:25.073 --> 00:13:32.163
This is Sahaja Yoga. In Sahaja Yoga there's
nothing to do with money or anything else.

00:13:32.264 --> 00:13:38.264
It's a very simple thing: that
we have this power within us,
which awakens.

00:13:38.453 --> 00:13:45.473
And it also gives us union with
that Great Power.

00:13:45.473 --> 00:13:50.912
This is your right because you are seekers.
What all you have done for God,

00:13:51.123 --> 00:13:54.813
so you have the right to achieve all
of this.

00:13:55.260 --> 00:14:04.220
And after having received this, in
your home, in your society, what
to say, in your ...

00:14:04.220 --> 00:14:11.072
