flowers have come into the world,

00:14:23.501 --> 00:14:30.321
But now, somehow, these should
become the fruit.

00:14:30.321 --> 00:14:36.819
And this time has come. Because of
this time, because of this special time...

00:14:42.909 --> 00:14:49.489
Your well-being is being achieved only
because of this time. I have no
special role in this.

00:14:49.489 --> 00:14:56.180
Everyone has done all the work in
their own times, and today is the
work of awakening which I am doing.

00:14:56.239 --> 00:14:59.749
If you ask Me to do it, I do it;
otherwise, I don't do it.

00:14:59.933 --> 00:15:08.513
Everything is happening on its own. Thus,
one small thing should be understood.

00:15:08.821 --> 00:15:11.931
There can be no pressure on anyone
in this.

00:15:13.482 --> 00:15:17.782
You have complete freedom, you may
go to Hell or go to Heaven.

00:15:17.859 --> 00:15:22.939
No one can stop you from doing this.
God has given you some freedom after all.

00:15:22.939 --> 00:15:26.842
Animals are in the bondage of God,
but you have freedom.

00:15:26.842 --> 00:15:30.571
If you want you can go to Hell, or
you can go to Heaven, if you want.

00:15:30.700 --> 00:15:33.300
So there can be no compulsion.
- that's the first thing.

00:15:33.300 --> 00:15:38.486
And the second thing is that you
should not think wrong(negative)
things about yourself.

00:15:38.486 --> 00:15:42.745
Many people might have said to you,
"You are a great sinner, you did this, you" -

00:15:42.745 --> 00:15:49.291
There's no such thing. After all,
you're human, and humans do make
mistakes. You're not God.

00:15:49.933 --> 00:15:53.133
So lowering(degrading) yourself in
some way, or

00:15:53.133 --> 00:15:58.462
saying things like, "What am I, how will
I get it, Mother," etc. is very wrong.

00:16:00.102 --> 00:16:07.002
You should think that, "If I have come
as a human being,"

00:16:07.159 --> 00:16:13.189
