it, why shouldn't I receive it?"

00:16:13.329 --> 00:16:16.679
And I'm telling you repeatedly that
you have a right.

00:16:17.495 --> 00:16:23.785
In this entire system created by God,
today is such a time,

00:16:23.785 --> 00:16:30.101
that the Satyayug has now begun. This
work is bound to happen in it, and that's
why you are receiving it.

00:16:30.101 --> 00:16:36.333
