you have done in your previous lives
that you are here today.

00:16:36.333 --> 00:16:46.105
And whatever virtuous deeds you have
done, are bearing fruit today;
you are benefiting from them.

00:16:47.158 --> 00:16:57.448
So, a kind of faith towards yourself,
a kind of belief, and especially
this desire in your heart,

00:16:57.448 --> 00:17:04.923
that, 'I should have self-realization.'
And will happen only through faith.
That's how everything happens.

00:17:05.234 --> 00:17:09.164
Have complete faith in yourself and
this thing will happen.

00:17:09.364 --> 00:17:15.974
